I" <p>Rogerio Bonatti is a Ph.D. student. His research focuses at the intersection of machine learning theory with motion planning, where he creates methods for robust robot intelligence in real-world settings. His work has been deployed for multiple applications, ranging from autonomous cinematography with aerial vehicles all the way to drone racing. He holds a Bachelors degree in Mechatronics Engineering from the University of Sao Paulo, Brazil.</p>

